name: MoHA Interactive Collection: featured artist souvenir sweatshirt
description: A souvenir sweatshirt gifted to the artists whose work features in the Museum of HEN Artfkts Interactive Collection. The collection holds some of the best interactive generative art, tools, toys, games and experimental OBJKTs of HEN and can be found at hecticnun.xyz/moha-interactive/collection. The permanent historical ARTFKT collection is at hic.art/moha
